    • Class Table extends java.lang.Object implements Serializable

      • Serialized Fields

        • availabilityRecord

          java.util.HashMap<java.time.LocalDate,​java.lang.Boolean[]> availabilityRecord
          Record of the Table's availability for Reservation as a map. Records are accessed by a LocalDate key, which will retrieve an array of boolean values that indicate the Table's availability. A true value indicates that the Table is available for Reservation, while a false value indicates that it is not. The array length is 24, in order to mimic 24 hours in a day which the Customer can book.

        • capacity

          int capacity
          Capacity of the Table.
